  "description": "A stunning panoramic view of a city bathed in the warm glow of a vibrant sunset. The sun is positioned low on the horizon, creating a radiant halo effect and casting long shadows across the urban landscape. The sky is a fiery spectacle of orange, yellow, and red hues, layered with dramatic cloud formations. In the distance, rolling hills and a calm body of water add depth to the composition. The city below is a grid of illuminated buildings, contrasting with the natural beauty of the surrounding environment. Silhouetted trees in the foreground frame the scene, providing a sense of perspective and scale. The overall effect is one of tranquility and awe.",
